Bossard Holding Logo Bossard Group is an internationally active Swiss fastener technology and logistics company with its headquarters in Zug. Their activities include worldwide sales, technical advice and inventory management. The Group employs around 2,500 employees at 83 locations in Europe, America and Asia/Pacific and in 2020 generated a turnover of 812.8 million Swiss francs. Bossard Group is listed on the Swiss Stock Exchange SIX Swiss Exchange. Source
